==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Troubler
<hw>Trou"bler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who troubles or
disturbs; one who afflicts or molests; a disturber; <as>as, a
<ex>troubler</ex> of the peace</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The rich <qex>troublers</qex> of the world's repose.</q>
<rj><qau>Waller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Troublesome</ent>⟦br⟧
